{"article_id":"d015BJUkgzEsbDWD","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A few days before Washington staggered into what would become the longest shutdown in U.S. history ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"Chuck Schumer received a request from Donald Trump .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"The president wanted the Senate minority leader to visit the White House","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"to discuss his demands for the border wall ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"which would need Democratic votes","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to pass the GOP-controlled Senate .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Previously , Schumer had held one-on-one negotiations with Trump .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"But this time , the New York Democrat had a new condition :","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"\" Only with Nancy . \"","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"\" We do it all together ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that ' s an agreement","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"we had from the get-go , \"","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Schumer said of his stance with Speaker Nancy Pelosi","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"on not giving Trump an inch on the wall .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"\" We realize","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"we ' re a team , \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Schumer said in an interview .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"\" Sometimes we talk strategy four to five times a day .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"And there are times","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"we disagree .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"But we come to the same result . \"","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Republicans have tried to drive a wedge between the duo for more than a month now .","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"They ' ve cast Schumer as eager to cut a deal","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"and Pelosi as an impediment .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"They ' ve floated the idea","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"that Pelosi would be more willing to compromise","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"after she was elected speaker .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Trump tried again on Saturday ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"pitching temporary protections for Dreamers and other immigrants , in exchange for $ 5.7 billion in border wall funding .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"Democrats believe","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"the only way","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"to get the president to cave on the wall and reopen the government","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"is to stick together , a plan","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"they reiterated","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"when they rejected Trump 's latest proposal .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"And","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"by setting a model of unity ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Schumer and Pelosi have kept moderates in their caucuses from breaking ranks","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"and underscored how difficult it will be for Trump to get Democrats to fold .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"From House freshmen in districts","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Trump won in 2016","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"to centrist Senate Democrats like Joe Manchin of West Virginia , they ' ve all said :","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Open the government ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"then let ' s talk about the border .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Republicans say","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"that rank-and-file Democrats are more eager to break from their leaders","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"than they let on","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"and have been frustrated by the party ' s lockstep opposition .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"\" Every one of them has an election certificate ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and it ' s not signed by Chuck Schumer and Nancy Pelosi .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"So do what you think is right , \"","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Sen. Lisa Murkowski","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"( R-Alaska )","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"said .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"But with a combined 70 years of service on Capitol Hill , the two are the experienced , old-school pols","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"that many Democrats want","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"leading them against a volatile and capricious president .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"That ' s even as Schumer and Pelosi , 68 and 78 respectively , diverge in some ways from their party ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"which is more diverse and younger than ever .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"though the Democratic leaders came up in the House together ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"represent liberal coastal areas","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"and even were part of the same dinner group years ago ,","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"their approach to politics often differs .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Schumer tends to slouch","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"when the cameras are turned off","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"and brings leftovers into the Senate each week .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Pelosi has become something of a fashion icon ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"clad in tailored pantsuits or dresses , often with matching high heels .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"One of Pelosi ' s coats even took on a life of its own","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"- resulting in the designer bringing it back","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"because of overwhelming demand -","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"after she wore it","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"to tangle with Trump in January .","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"Schumer fashions himself a messaging and political guru","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"and is known for ingratiating himself with his members .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"He was accused by liberals of not whipping his moderate members hard enough last year against GOP priorities ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"but consolidated power internally","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"by giving centrists an opportunity","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"to craft their own political images .","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"Pelosi hails from a Baltimore political dynasty","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"and is more of a blunt operator .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"She also deals with internal critics swiftly and efficiently ;","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"she blocked Rep. Kathleen Rice","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"( D-N.Y. )","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"from a plum committee spot","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"for having tried to oust her as party leader , for example .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"\" It ' s a magical odd couple , \"","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Sen. Richard Blumenthal","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"( D-Conn. )","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"said .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"\" Very different backgrounds , different religions , different manners , different physical appearances .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"He ' s the Jewish Brooklyn guy ;","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"she is the West Coast ,","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"you know ,","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"sort of glamorous hobnobbing with movie stars . \"","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"During Trump ' s first two years , Pelosi would often defer to her Senate counterpart ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"who had the ability","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"to filibuster GOP legislation .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"As the new House speaker , Pelosi ' s effectively canceling Trump ' s State of the Union address .","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"With Pelosi now the top Democrat in Washington , \" the dynamic is changing , \"","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"said one lawmaker with insight into the relationship between the two party leaders .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"Pelosi and Schumer appear to be managing the shift in power relatively well .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"But their tag-team leadership style has at times opened them up to criticism .","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"When they learned","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"that Trump would give a prime-time address on the border wall earlier this month ,","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Pelosi and Schumer connected immediately .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"They ruled out picking a rank-and-file member or young , rising Democratic star","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"to push back against Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"ignoring those","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"who noted","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"the two leaders aren ' t the most dynamic speakers in the party .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"though Pelosi now outranks Schumer ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"they decided","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"they ' d do it together .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"They were the ones","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"who had spent hours with Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"and they would be the best at responding to him .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"\" Why not pick someone else ?","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"Because you had to do it very quickly ,","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"we didn ' t know","depth":16},{"id":122,"text":"what he was going to say , \"","depth":16},{"id":123,"text":"Schumer recalled .","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"\" We knew him best","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"and what he would say","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"and what he had said before . \"","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"Still , their response to Trump sparked laughs","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"as they shared a podium ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"staring unsmiling and stiffly at the camera .","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"\" Oh , my God , \"","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"said one freshman Democrat .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"\" Visually , it wasn ' t the best idea . \"","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"\" It did look funny ,","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"there was no doubt about it , ''","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"said Rep. Juan Vargas","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"( D-Calif. ) ,","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"expressing a sentiment","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"shared by many Democrats .","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"`` American Gothic , '' the painting by artist Grant Wood , was one of the frequent comparisons","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"- and not only on Twitter .","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"\" Grant Wood was at that podium , \"","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"Sen. Sherrod Brown","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"( D-Ohio )","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"said .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"\" Was that a meme too ?","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"I guess","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"it had to be .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"It was too obvious . \"","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"Yet they earned better TV ratings than Trump","depth":4},{"id":150,"text":"and reinforced","depth":5},{"id":151,"text":"that there would be no split between them .","depth":5},{"id":152,"text":"Their strategy sessions have centered on more than just optics .","depth":4},{"id":153,"text":"Schumer has frequently crossed the Capitol","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"to join in House Democratic leadership meetings and huddles with the wider caucus .","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"After the Senate passed a bill","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"guaranteeing back pay for furloughed and unpaid federal workers ,","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"Schumer asked Pelosi","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"if she would take up the Senate bill","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"to avoid having to reconcile it with a separate House measure","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"and she agreed ,","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"according to two people familiar with their conversations .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"Trump signed the bill soon after .","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"The two also consulted","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"before Pelosi began having the House pass piecemeal bills","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"to reopen parts of the government ;","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"Schumer told her","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"he liked the idea ,","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"reasoning","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"it would put more pressure on McConnell ,","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"those people said .","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"\" They trust one another ,","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"they value one another ' s judgment , \"","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"Dick Durbin of Illinois , the No . 2 Senate Democrat , said .","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"\" She is the lead Democrat by virtue of her title and majority status , \"","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"Rep. Gerry Connolly","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"( D-Va. )","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"said .","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"\" He kind of is playing the role of wingman right now ,","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"[ but ] I think","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"Chuck is a pro","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"and I think","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"he understands roles ebb and flow . \"","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"With Democrats in control of the House","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"and wielding the filibuster in the Senate ,","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"Trump ' s legislative agenda is at the mercy of Pelosi and Schumer","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"- as long as they remain united .","depth":6},{"id":187,"text":"\" It forces Republicans to think differently about their strategy","depth":7},{"id":188,"text":"if they see Nancy and Chuck as a unit for the next two years , \"","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"Sen. Chris Murphy","depth":8},{"id":190,"text":"( D-Conn. ) ,","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"a former House member , said .","depth":7},{"id":192,"text":"The shutdown fight started with some intraparty division .","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"Pelosi ' s members were frustrated","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"that Schumer ' s Senate was advocating for $ 1.6 billion in border fencing , part of a bipartisan deal","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"hatched in the summer .","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"House Democrats wanted $ 1.3 billion ,","depth":9},{"id":197,"text":"freezing spending at current levels .","depth":9},{"id":198,"text":"Quietly after the midterms , Schumer canned the higher number .","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":200,"text":"it could not pass the House .","depth":10},{"id":201,"text":"And that was that .","depth":8},{"id":202,"text":"Ever since , Pelosi and Schumer have earned the nickname","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"Trump bestowed ,","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"`` Chuck and Nancy , ''","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"even though it might be more appropriate these days for Pelosi 's name to go first .","depth":8},{"id":206,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":9},{"id":207,"text":"the speaker of the House or Senate minority leader are concerned about their power .","depth":9},{"id":208,"text":"They ' re both very secure in who they are , \"","depth":8},{"id":209,"text":"Rep. Ro Khanna","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"( D-Calif. )","depth":9},{"id":211,"text":"said .","depth":8},{"id":212,"text":"\" People with real power don ' t have to flex power . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":425,"left":308,"right":424,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":233,"right":307,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":218,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":214,"right":217,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":217,"left":2,"right":216,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":3,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":225,"right":231,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":220,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":6,"right":219,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":219,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":224,"left":9,"right":223,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":221,"right":222,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":10,"